.SH NAME
.PP
vedv-image-build - Build an image from a Vedvfile
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
vedv image build [FLAGS] [OPTIONS] VEDVFILE
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Build an image from a Vedvfile
.SH ALIASES
.PP
vedv builder build
.SH FLAGS
.TP
\f[V]-h, --help\f[R]
Show the help
.TP
\f[V]--force\f[R]
Force the build removing the image containers
.TP
\f[V]--no-cache\f[R]
Do not use cache when building the image
.TP
\f[V]--no-wait\f[R]
It will not wait for the image to stop after build
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\f[V]-n, --name <name>\f[R]
Image name
